{"tid":2340483,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"如何關心驚青貓貓？","createTime":"2020-12-25T13:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T10:05:05.000Z","uid":11382,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"bd097541910273430d70289eddf87f376343caf6","tid":2340483,"uid":11382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:20:59.000Z","msg":"大家好呀，我到而家都未成功正面摸到隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n養左隻貓一個月都未掂到佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2294358\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2294358</a><br />\n<br />\n而家我同隻貓既關係就停留係餵食既關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朝早佢會走去床邊喵醒我叫我加糧，但我一起身就會躲埋<br />\n貓貓最鐘意躲係櫃後面既貓窩，貪我地難摸佢<br />\n我而家間中會拎不求人去幫佢梳下毛，佢都肯既<br />\n但一試下伸隻手指埋去就會縮後，再伸前就拍<br />\n因為我地無成功剪過爪既關係，佢一拍就好易見血<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外有時屋企會有朋友上黎，佢一見朋友黎就縮得更埋<br />\n直頭縮到間房啲角落位，我地都係等佢自己驚完出返黎<br />\n<br />\n我有買過啲費洛蒙個啲但好似無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我開始唔知應該繼續積極咁同隻貓玩定由佢靜下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f00d78a33fedab80536091de1645425eeeb05d","tid":2340483,"uid":125303,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:24:26.000Z","msg":"困籠親訓到唔驚人為止"},{"pid":"22cc4cf2b63ce58fc3f29cbcb3aeb53044e6edb1","tid":2340483,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:26:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fb8be2dad659479013140cb5761f4832547c024","tid":2340483,"uid":383298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T13:44:52.000Z","msg":"貓草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fce505f55d594335c0d53d3edd2622f4a3fc7cb","tid":2340483,"uid":58867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:30:50.000Z","msg":"肉球好正"},{"pid":"2c7cc9b65738424ba4991a5c558a7fe658fef614","tid":2340483,"uid":111322,"like":9,"dislike":0,